{"id":556540,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/04/【立此存照】绝对忠诚：刊发新华社通稿的艺术/","date":"2017-04-14T07:30:28Z","modified":"2017-04-14T07:31:10Z","title":"【立此存照】绝对忠诚：刊发新华社通稿的艺术","content":"<blockquote><p><a href=\"http://weibo.com/2472331131/EEs7LntHv?refer_flag=1001030103_&amp;type=comment#_rnd1492152716154\" target=\"_blank\">@孙月沐</a>：今天各大报的头版头条标题，光明日报经济日报等处理成“千年大计 国家大事”是对的，中间无须用顿号，因为空字符在此处起顿号作用。而人民日报解放军报等在标题中用顿号是蛇足的，既不美，又多余，估计新华社发通稿时就是这样。 ​</p></blockquote>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/935cc77bly1fem3k7tpd4j20zk0qoqe8.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-556542\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/935cc77bly1fem3k7tpd4j20zk0qoqe8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/935cc77bly1fem3k7tpd4j20zk0qoqe8.jpg 1280w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/935cc77bly1fem3k7tpd4j20zk0qoqe8-300x225.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/935cc77bly1fem3k7tpd4j20zk0qoqe8-768x576.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/935cc77bly1fem3k7tpd4j20zk0qoqe8-1024x768.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2015/12/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%bf%bd%e5%a6%82%e4%b8%80%e5%a4%9c%e6%98%a5%e9%a3%8e%e6%9d%a5%ef%bc%8c%e5%8d%83%e6%8a%a5%e4%b8%87%e6%8a%a5%e9%a9%ac%e5%b7%b4/\" target=\"_blank\">【立此存照】忽如一夜春风来，千报万报“马巴”开</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><strong>新华社通稿原文的确使用了顿号：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_556541\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/新华社.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-556541\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/新华社.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"394\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/新华社.jpg 1590w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/新华社-300x237.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/新华社-768x606.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/新华社-1024x808.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">网页截图</span></p></div>\n<p><strong>中央级报纸在刊发新华社通稿时，照搬顿号的有：《人民日报》、《解放军报》、《工人日报》、《法制日报》</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒顿号组.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-556544\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒顿号组.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"727\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒顿号组.jpg 1998w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒顿号组-206x300.jpg 206w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒顿号组-768x1117.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒顿号组-704x1024.jpg 704w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>用空格代替顿号的有：《光明日报》、《经济日报》、《中国青年报》</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒空格组.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-556543\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒空格组.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒空格组.jpg 4093w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒空格组-300x146.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒空格组-768x375.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/央媒空格组-1024x500.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>地方媒体基本都用了空格替代顿号：</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/地方报纸空格组.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-556545\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/地方报纸空格组.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"935\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/地方报纸空格组.jpg 4999w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/地方报纸空格组-193x300.jpg 193w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/地方报纸空格组-768x1197.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/地方报纸空格组-657x1024.jpg 657w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>&#8230;除了《四川日报》。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/四川日报.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-556546\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/四川日报.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"574\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/四川日报.jpg 836w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/四川日报-209x300.jpg 209w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/四川日报-768x1102.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/四川日报-713x1024.jpg 713w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,19168,27949],"tags":[9458,30319,23589,10702,18847,26988]}